1
00:00:15,199 --> 00:00:16,000
Miss

2
00:00:17,480 --> 00:00:18,280
Miss

3
00:00:19,039 --> 00:00:19,839
Wake up

4
00:00:21,239 --> 00:00:21,839
We're here

5
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:24,079
Sir

6
00:00:24,879 --> 00:00:26,079
Looks like it's about to rain

7
00:00:26,079 --> 00:00:27,679
Could you take me a bit further?

8
00:00:27,679 --> 00:00:28,600
Just drive on in

9
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:29,839
Thanks

10
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:33,880
It's an urban village in there.

11
00:00:34,679 --> 00:00:35,479
Hard to park there

12
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,479
Fine, how much?

13
00:00:40,079 --> 00:00:40,679
Twenty-eight

14
00:00:48,840 --> 00:00:49,560
Keep the change

15
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,879
He must have seen me hit someone.

16
00:01:49,519 --> 00:01:51,239
After he drove past me,

17
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:53,079
he, he stopped.

18
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:55,640
I really saw that woman get in that taxi.

19
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,239
What was the plate number?

20
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,079
I can't remember.

21
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,040
I was in a rush to get home.

22
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,400
I'm being framed!

23
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,239
I really didn't do anything.

24
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:12,199
Was there a wound near Liu Xiang's navel?

25
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:13,719
Yes, there was one.

26
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:15,080
Show me the photo.

27
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:17,719
But it's not very obvious.

28
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,319
Looks like a wound from a sharp object.

29
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,719
It could also be that during the body dump,

30
00:02:21,919 --> 00:02:23,199
she was scraped by something sharp.

31
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,479
Red Gloves.

32
00:02:29,680 --> 00:02:30,680
It must be Red Gloves.

33
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,800
Boss, you mean

34
00:02:34,159 --> 00:02:36,159
this case was also done by Red Gloves?

35
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:51,000
Sorry, the number you dialed is not answering.

36
00:03:14,199 --> 00:03:16,439
Although a taxi appeared at Liu Xiang's crime scene,

37
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:18,719
there were no carvings on her body.

38
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:20,520
This wound was likely made by a knife.

39
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:22,360
Look at this wound.

40
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,280
Doesn't it look like a stroke of a character?

41
00:03:28,919 --> 00:03:30,560
A twisted personality like Red Gloves

42
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:33,120
seeks the ultimate perverse thrill.

43
00:03:34,159 --> 00:03:35,800
The more the victim struggles,

44
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,680
the more it ignites his savage lust.

45
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,599
He must have been carving the character

46
00:03:41,599 --> 00:03:43,000
when he realized the victim was already dead.

47
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:49,960
Hello?

48
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:51,639
Hello, Brother Li.

49
00:03:51,639 --> 00:03:52,199
Where's my brother?

50
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,280
Why isn't he answering his phone?

51
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,719
He promised he'd come pick me up.

52
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,400
He went to gather evidence.

53
00:03:56,599 --> 00:03:57,400
He should be back soon.

54
00:03:57,719 --> 00:04:00,120
No, that taxi just now was so terrifying.

55
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,960
That driver's eyes were so creepy.

56
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,479
And he was wearing red gloves.

57
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,639
Red Gloves?

58
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:06,840
Where are you?

59
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:07,800
Xingfu Village.

60
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:12,400
Ruolan, run! Run, now!

61
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,240
Ruolan! Ruolan!

62
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,639
Xingfu Village. Red Gloves has shown up.

63
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:32,519
Ruolan is in danger.

64
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,600
Ruolan? Who's Ruolan, Boss?

65
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:11,040
Boss

66
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,839
Who exactly is this Ruolan?

67
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:14,079
Captain Zhao's little sister.

68
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:15,920
Their parents passed away from illness,

69
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:18,120
leaving the two siblings to rely on each other.

70
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:38,920
Who's there?

71
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:40,079
Who's over there?

72
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,199
Boss

73
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,319
This is the phone Captain Zhao gave Ruolan

74
00:09:50,159 --> 00:09:50,799
She's inside.

75
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:52,080
Inside.

76
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,240
Ruolan.

77
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:03,840
Go check

78
00:10:04,759 --> 00:10:05,720
if Captain Zhao has arrived.

79
00:10:21,399 --> 00:10:23,000
Captain Zhao, you're finally here.

80
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,360
Your sister's in the back room.

81
00:10:38,759 --> 00:10:39,399
Boss.

82
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,360
Ruolan.

83
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:54,759
Don't touch me!

84
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:57,639
Ruolan.

85
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:58,279
Don't touch me!

86
00:10:58,519 --> 00:10:59,320
Don't you touch me!

87
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:00,399
Ruolan.

88
00:11:00,399 --> 00:11:01,120
Don't touch me!

89
00:11:01,120 --> 00:11:02,080
It's me, your brother.

90
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:02,679
Don't touch me!

91
00:11:02,679 --> 00:11:03,480
Ruolan.

92
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:04,960
Ruolan.

93
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:06,360
It's me, your brother.

94
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,679
Open your eyes and look at me.

95
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,320
It's me, your brother.

96
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,120
I'm taking you home.

97
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:51,960
Don't run!

98
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:56,639
Stop right there!

99
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:12,559
Get up

100
00:13:16,879 --> 00:13:17,759
Why are you getting up?

101
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,200
You're hurt, just rest.

102
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,720
I'm sorry, Boss.

103
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,960
I almost caught Red Gloves.

104
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,559
How do you know it was Red Gloves?

105
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,360
He was wearing red gloves.

106
00:13:32,679 --> 00:13:34,399
Matches the victim's description.

107
00:13:34,919 --> 00:13:36,200
Isn't that the best proof

108
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:38,279
that criminals return to the scene?

109
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,320
What car was he driving?

110
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:46,480
That bastard caught me off guard with a tranquilizer dart.

111
00:13:47,679 --> 00:13:48,440
I didn't get a clear look.

112
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,799
It's my fault for underestimating him.

113
00:13:52,519 --> 00:13:53,039
Enough.

114
00:13:53,759 --> 00:13:54,919
Beating yourself up won't help.

115
00:13:56,799 --> 00:13:57,679
Remember this from now on.

116
00:13:59,679 --> 00:14:00,960
Unless you're absolutely certain,

117
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,360
don't act alone.

118
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:03,919
No suspect is going to care

119
00:14:03,919 --> 00:14:05,240
whether you're a Fighting Champion.

120
00:14:05,639 --> 00:14:06,720
The moment you underestimate them,

121
00:14:07,320 --> 00:14:08,480
they'll kill you in a heartbeat.

122
00:14:09,159 --> 00:14:09,840
Understand?

123
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:13,559
Even though he was covered up tightly,

124
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,039
from what I observed,

125
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:16,440
he's likely a young male.

126
00:14:16,919 --> 00:14:18,279
And he has some fighting skills.

127
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,720
A young male...

128
00:14:23,399 --> 00:14:24,000
Mm.

129
00:14:25,120 --> 00:14:25,799
Boss,

130
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:29,480
what's your connection to the Red Gloves of Case 531?

131
00:14:31,679 --> 00:14:32,600
The way I see it,

132
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,480
this is purely a coincidence.

133
00:14:34,919 --> 00:14:37,399
Even if Red Gloves did exist, he'd be long dead.

134
00:14:42,879 --> 00:14:44,840
Don't end up like my dad.

135
00:15:07,039 --> 00:15:07,600
Captain Li.

136
00:15:08,679 --> 00:15:09,440
Anything, Fei?

137
00:15:10,399 --> 00:15:11,720
Apart from a few shoeprints,

138
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,240
no other traces were found.

139
00:15:26,639 --> 00:15:27,399
Ruolan.

140
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:35,600
Ruolan.

141
00:15:38,159 --> 00:15:40,279
I made your favorite, braised chicken legs.

142
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:41,960
Come out and eat something.

143
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,799
I'm not hungry.

144
00:16:07,879 --> 00:16:08,840
I promise you, sis,

145
00:16:13,879 --> 00:16:15,799
I'll catch that bastard, no matter what.
